title: United Kingdom 52 Week Bill Yield
description: UK 1 Year Bond Yield was 3.10 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 52 Week Bill Yield reached an all time high of 6.19 in November of 2007. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 52W.
